{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"98325660f4","title":"纵火者","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c4c0994962","index":0,"year":1957,"month":7,"day":null,"articleId":"98325660f4"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"a8442473a7","name":"徐迟"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"10a4e9da2f","type":"title","text":"纵火者","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98325660f4"},{"id":"14e3ca9ebb","type":"authors","text":"徐迟","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98325660f4"},{"id":"f1b444d094","type":"paragraph","text":"解放以前，你本是个官僚，          夺取领导的计谋已成，","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98325660f4"},{"id":"9bc13fd47b","type":"paragraph","text":"解放以后，你官儿又不小，          哪知风向火势忽的一转。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98325660f4"},{"id":"58f2a7935c","type":"paragraph","text":"盟里一“长”，机关里一“长”，","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98325660f4"},{"id":"3fc918c656","type":"paragraph","text":"我们还恭请你当我们的代表。        昨天还趾高气扬，","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98325660f4"},{"id":"d7fe55c693","type":"paragraph","text":"今天却灰溜溜的检讨：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98325660f4"},{"id":"17d55a7739","type":"paragraph","text":"谁知你是一条披羊皮的狼，          我犯了个严重错误，","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98325660f4"},{"id":"b79d67292f","type":"paragraph","text":"想不到你是一个纵火者。            我立场不稳，认识模糊。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98325660f4"},{"id":"da040eda8b","type":"paragraph","text":"你的舌尖上喷出火花，","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98325660f4"},{"id":"db995e3168","type":"paragraph","text":"要火烧共和国的大厦。              昨天还是张牙舞爪一条龙，","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98325660f4"},{"id":"7f74d7a856","type":"paragraph","text":"今天是耗子，只恨地下没有洞，","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98325660f4"},{"id":"a4c4ff56f9","type":"paragraph","text":"借口积极帮助共产党，              前倨后恭，假检讨的把戏，","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98325660f4"},{"id":"79edb35052","type":"paragraph","text":"你把火点着，把它煽旺，            资产阶级政客演的十分成功。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98325660f4"},{"id":"6819ead7e0","type":"paragraph","text":"刮上一阵风，浇上一桶油，","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98325660f4"},{"id":"d5c8ed46ad","type":"paragraph","text":"希望大火能够燎原。                告诉你，烧起来的火焰，","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98325660f4"},{"id":"c132605cad","type":"paragraph","text":"扑灭它真是不容易，","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98325660f4"},{"id":"4152f054ae","type":"paragraph","text":"强盗忽然发善心，你说，            共和国的大厦巍然无恙，","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98325660f4"},{"id":"c5df7e66f3","type":"paragraph","text":"说到救火，舍你还有谁？            烧只烧那些纵火的罪犯。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98325660f4"},{"id":"7a9b6666be","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：  《诗刊杂志--反右派斗争特辑》，诗刊社，1957年7月。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98325660f4"}],"page":{"id":"35bb0bac9c","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98325660f4","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}